                <h2>Clinical Treatments That Actually Deliver Results</h2>
                <p>When home remedies and dietary changes are not sufficient, clinical treatments can be a game-changer. At DenceSpot Clinic, we offer several proven treatments:</p>

                <h3>1. PRP Therapy — Your Blood, Your Growth Factors</h3>
                <p><a href="../hair-prp-treatment-in-gurgaon">PRP (Platelet-Rich Plasma) treatment in Gurgaon</a> is a revolutionary procedure in which growth factors extracted from your own blood are injected into the scalp. This activates dormant follicles and stimulates <strong>fast hair growth</strong>. Visible improvement is typically observed within 3 to 4 sessions. You can learn about the entire process in our <a href="prp-hair-treatment-natural-way-to-regrow-hair.php">detailed PRP guide</a>.</p>

                <h3>2. Microneedling — Revitalizing the Scalp</h3>
                <p><a href="../hair-microneedling-in-gurgaon">Microneedling treatment in Gurgaon</a> involves creating micro-channels on the scalp using tiny needles. This triggers the body's natural wound healing response, boosts collagen production, and promotes the release of growth factors. When combined with PRP, the results are even more impressive.</p>

                <h3>3. LED Therapy — Harnessing Light for Growth</h3>
